	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I guess you're right, but my biggest fear of NES development is the lack of an interface, and how everything must seemingly be done directly to the metal.  As for unused features, can't you just cut them out from the final game?  Or is it much easier said than done?<br /><br />And regarding 8-way scrolling, is there any other way to do it in an artifact free way, aside from hiding them with sprites or a black bar?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
